title: Jack Black says Tenacious D will jazz things up for its third Festival Supreme this weekend
text: Jack Black says Tenacious D will jazz things up for its third Festival Supreme this weekend Oct. 7, 2015 Updated 4:14 p.m. 1 of 6 Kyle Gass (left) and Jack Black of Tenacious D bring their third annual Festival Supreme comedy, music and more show back to the Shrine Expo Hall & Grounds in Los Angeles on Saturday. , ASA MOORE 1 of 6 Jack Black (right) and Kyle Gass (left) of Tenacious D played a rockin' set at KROQ 106.7 FM's annual April Foolishness earlier this year, but the D will be offering a special performance for fans at its Festival Supreme at the Shrine Expo Hall & Grounds in Los Angeles on Saturday by doing a jazz-filled set. , KELLY A. SWIFT, CONTRIBUTING PHOTOGRAPHER 1 of 6 Rock musician Andrew W.K. will perform a solo set at the third annual Festival Supreme at the Shrine Expo Hall & Grounds in Los Angeles on Saturday. ASHLEY EBERBACH 1 of 6 Jack Black of Tenacious D played a rockin' set at KROQ 106.7 FM's annual April Foolishness earlier this year, but the D will be offering a special performance for fans at its Festival Supreme at the Shrine Expo Hall & Grounds in Los Angeles on Saturday by doing a jazz-filled set. KELLY A. SWIFT, CONTRIBUTING PHOTOGRAPHER 1 of 6 Rock musician Andrew W.K. will perform a solo set at the third annual Festival Supreme at the Shrine Expo Hall & Grounds in Los Angeles on Saturday. ANDREW STRASSER 1 of 6 Jack Black (right) and Kyle Gass (left) of Tenacious D will headline its annual Festival Supreme at the Shrine Expo Hall & Grounds in Los Angeles on Saturday and be doing a jazz-filled set for fans. JACK PLUNKETT, ASSOCIATES PRESS
